| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2552 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: bddb6c08-1cc3-5f85-bf77-04135edd175c"
